snippet.title: AWOL Ahab (final trailer)
snippet.description:
AWOL Ahab is a retro styled shmup where every bullet fired lowers the score, but every enemy hit or destroyed raises the score.

Fly the Dolphin through an enemy invasion to find a ship capable of defeating the enemy boss.

Facebook - https://www.facebook.com/AWOLAhab/

Gamejolt - https://gamejolt.com/games/AWOL-Ahab/255145
Itch - https://methodcomix.itch.io/awol-ahab
